query:
SELECT 
    LOWER(TRIM(nome)) as nome_norm,
    cpf,
    COUNT(*) as qtd,
    GROUP_CONCAT(id_paciente SEPARATOR ', ') as ids
FROM pacientes 
WHERE deleted_at IS NULL 
    AND cpf IS NOT NULL 
    AND cpf != ''
    AND LENGTH(REPLACE(REPLACE(cpf, '.', ''), '-', '')) >= 11
GROUP BY LOWER(TRIM(nome)), cpf
HAVING COUNT(*) > 1
ORDER BY qtd DESC, nome_norm
LIMIT 50;
